WAP
1. Given an input string str of n length, find the number of consitives characters present in the given and delete those consitive chars in the string str. 
2. repeat the process untill all the consitive characters are deleted/removed from the given string i.e str.

3. find the number of the operation are done while deleting the consitive characters.

i/p
ZYABDFEC

o/p

